## Frontend Deep Dive

### Routing Structure

| Path | Component | Description |
|------|-----------|-------------|
| `/login` | Login | Email + password login |
| `/signup` | Signup | User registration |
| `/jobs` (default `/`) | Dashboard | SQL Agent job monitor |
| `/expenses` | Expenses | Expense vs Receipt audit |
| `/reconciliation` | Reconciliation | Concur vs LZ comparison |
| `/qdera` | QderaReconciliation | Qdera vs LZ comparison |
| `/flagcheck` | FlagCheck | Data flag validation |
| `/receipt-categorization` | ReceiptCategorization | Receipt type analysis |

All routes except `/login` and `/signup` are wrapped in `ProtectedRoute` → `Layout`.

### API Layer

- [axios.js](file:///c:/Users/afzal.sharif/OneDrive%20-%20Qordata/Desktop/visual/ema/frontend/my-app/src/api/axios.js) — Base URL `http://localhost:5000/api`, auto-attaches JWT from `localStorage`, auto-redirects to `/login` on 401
- [queries.js](file:///c:/Users/afzal.sharif/OneDrive%20-%20Qordata/Desktop/visual/ema/frontend/my-app/src/api/queries.js) — 12 query functions mapping to backend endpoints, all following the same URLSearchParams filter pattern

### Shared Components

| Component | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| **Layout** | App shell with sidebar navigation + main content area |
| **DateFilter** | Reusable filter component supporting Today/Date/Month/Year/Range modes |
| **Toast** | Context-based notification system with ToastProvider |
| **ProtectedRoute** | Checks `localStorage` for token before rendering children |

### Dashboard Page (Largest — 1046 lines)

The [Dashboard.jsx](file:///c:/Users/afzal.sharif/OneDrive%20-%20Qordata/Desktop/visual/ema/frontend/my-app/src/pages/Dashboard/Dashboard.jsx) is the most complex page:

- **Helper functions**: [hhmmssToSecs()](file:///c:/Users/afzal.sharif/OneDrive%20-%20Qordata/Desktop/visual/ema/frontend/my-app/src/pages/Dashboard/Dashboard.jsx#36-41), [formatRunTime()](file:///c:/Users/afzal.sharif/OneDrive%20-%20Qordata/Desktop/visual/ema/frontend/my-app/src/pages/Dashboard/Dashboard.jsx#43-55) (UTC→PKT conversion), [formatDuration()](file:///c:/Users/afzal.sharif/OneDrive%20-%20Qordata/Desktop/visual/ema/frontend/my-app/src/pages/Dashboard/Dashboard.jsx#56-67), [buildStepPipeline()](file:///c:/Users/afzal.sharif/OneDrive%20-%20Qordata/Desktop/visual/ema/frontend/my-app/src/pages/Dashboard/Dashboard.jsx#68-103)
- **Data fetching**: Uses `useQuery` for stats, running jobs, and scheduled jobs
- **Visualization**: Recharts `BarChart` + `PieChart` for status distribution
- **Interactivity**: Expandable job rows → run details → step pipelines
- **Features**: Insert new jobs button, client filter, date filter, auto-refresh

