## Data Flow Diagram

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant R as React Frontend
    participant A as Axios API Layer
    participant E as Express Backend
    participant M as MSSQL Server
    participant C as Client Databases

    U->>R: Navigate to /expenses
    R->>A: fetchExpenseStats(filters)
    A->>E: GET /api/expenses/stats?dateType=submit&date=2026-03-02
    Note over A,E: JWT token attached via interceptor
    E->>M: Connect to EMA_Support_Module
    M-->>E: Connection pool
    E->>M: Discover enabled client DBs
    M-->>E: [ClientA_DB, ClientB_DB, ...]
    loop For each client DB
        E->>C: Dynamic SQL: INSERT INTO #temp SELECT FROM [ClientDB].[dbo].[LZ_table]
        C-->>E: Results accumulated in temp table
    end
    E->>M: SELECT summary + client stats + details FROM #temp
    M-->>E: Result sets
    E-->>A: JSON { summary, clientStats, detailRows }
    A-->>R: Parsed response
    R-->>U: Render charts + tables
```

---

## Known Issues & Performance Notes

From [PERFORMANCE_ANALYSIS.md](file:///c:/Users/afzal.sharif/OneDrive%20-%20Qordata/Desktop/visual/ema/PERFORMANCE_ANALYSIS.md):

| Issue | Impact | Status |
|-------|--------|--------|
| SQL `OUTER APPLY` with `LIKE` pattern matching | 70-80% of load time (30-60s) | Partially fixed (switched to `LEFT JOIN`) |
| No password hashing | Security risk | **Not fixed** |
| Frontend renders all rows without virtualization | Slow with 2,100+ rows | Not fixed |
| Hardcoded `localhost:5000` API URL | Won't work in production | Not fixed |
| No connection pooling management | Potential connection leaks | Not fixed |
| Request timeout set to 5 minutes | Long-running queries block | By design |

---

## How to Run

### Backend
```bash
cd backend
npm install
node server.js    # or: npx nodemon server.js
# Runs on port 5000
```

### Frontend
```bash
cd frontend/my-app
npm install
npm run dev
# Runs on port 5173 (Vite dev server)
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The backend requires network access to the MSSQL server at `52.88.29.244` with the credentials in [.env](file:///c:/Users/afzal.sharif/OneDrive%20-%20Qordata/Desktop/visual/ema/backend/.env).
